    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>285912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_000Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この街はずっと
こんな調子さ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This village has a pretty depressing
atmosphere to it, doesn't it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286036</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_001Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こんなに貧しいのに、
ここの人々は何の見返りもなく
僕を受け容れてくれた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Everyone suffers through poverty. Each person
gives me something to think about.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_002Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>僕はエルフだ。
だが、魔術が使えない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You know I'm an Elf, but despite that I can't use magic.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それって、
『レスネス』ってヤツ？
前に本で読んだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Does that mean you're a..."Lessneth"?
I've read about that in a book before.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286304</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>レス、ネス……？
何それ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Less...neth? What is that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286412</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔術使えないエルフ。
百年にひとりしか
生まれねんだって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They are Elves who can't use magic
One is born every 1000 years.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_006Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よく知っているね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You sure know a lot!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_007Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『レスネス』はエルフの里を
不幸にするとされていて、
生まれるとすぐ里を追い出される</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In the Elven village, Lessneths are considered
an omen of misfortune and sorrow. They're
banished right after being born.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、
バジルさんも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Does that mean that you...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_009Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう。居場所をなくした僕は
この街に流れついた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Precisely. Without anywhere to go, I
wandered and ended up in this village.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_010Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よそ者の僕にも
ここの人たちはよくしてくれた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>These people were used to strangers
like me and understood me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>286924</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、
アルヴァニスタじゃなくて
ここに？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So that's why you stayed here and not in Alvanista?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_012Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ。ここの方が
居心地がいいからね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, I feel more comfortable around here.
It's my true home.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_013Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それに、一番大切なことを
教えられる気がするんだ。
自分が今、何をするべきか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>More importantly, I think I've learned something priceless
here. I want to help this place as much as I can.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287180</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それが
魔術の研究？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I guess that's why you got into Magic Research?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_015Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>人も『レスネス』も関係なく、
魔術を使えるようになるための
技術の研究さ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Both humans and Lessneths can relate in that
they hope to find means to use magic. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_016Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔術がもっとなじめば、
きっとこの村を、いや世界を
もっと豊かにできるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If we're able to achieve that, people will have new 
possibilities... No...the entire world will change! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でっかい夢だな、それ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's one big dream...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_018Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どんな大きな夢でも
思い続けなければ叶わない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No matter how big your dream is, if your mind isn't set on
seeing it through to the end, you'll never make it a reality.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_019Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>信じることが
大切なんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Believing is the most important part.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>信じること、か。う～ん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>To believe...uhh.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287840</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_022Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君には
そういう夢はないのかい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't you have any dreams?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287924</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレ……？
オレはええっと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Me? I...um...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何かになりたい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I want to become everything!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288076</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何かって……
きみは、もう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Everything...? Your dream is...well...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃなくって！　どうすりゃいいかは
わかんねーけど、自分の足で
歩いてけるようになりたいんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey! I'm not entirely sure yet, but... With one
step at a time, anyone can do anything!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288284</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それで……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And um...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288452</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_028Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ハハッ、
ゆっくり考えればいいさ。
君の未来は真っ白だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haha! Thinking it over, your dream
is as noble as it can get. </EnglishText>
      <Notes>We changed it some but TL check pls</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288452</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_029Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君はまだ
どんなものにでも
なれるんだからさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You keep trying and you'll see.
You'll be able to do anything!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288536</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>真っ白……
どんなもんにでも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A noble dream... What do you mean...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_031Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>強く願い続ければ、
どんな気持ちでも叶う、
そう思うんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If your convictions are strong, your dream will
come true. Never forget your dream.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_032Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、
がんばれよ、&lt;Dio&gt;！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's why... Never give up, &lt;Dio&gt;! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288764</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、う、うん……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>R-Right!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_034Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>僕も人を応援している場合じゃ
ないんだけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In my case, not many people help me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_035Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、&lt;Claus&gt;もまた
やる気になってくれたし、
研究も進展すると思う。</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But knowing &lt;Claus&gt; is there, I'm sure
there'll always be progress.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>288992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_036Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔科学があれば
もう少し……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With a little more, Magitechnology will...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔科学？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Magitechnology?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_038Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ん？　いや……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh? It's nothing.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289200</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;、何をやってるんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Rody, what are you doing over there?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>39</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289292</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ん？　空がきれいだなって
見とれてたんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wh-What? I was taking some time
to admire the beauty of the sky.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さてと……どこか
泊まれるところを
借りられないだろうか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Anyhow, we need to find a place to stay for the night.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289492</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_042Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうか、よかったら、
うちを使ってくれ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're right. You can use this house over here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289616</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_043Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりともおはよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Good morning you two!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>43</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289616</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_044Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>アルヴァニスタから
返信があったよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alvanista has replied to us.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>43</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289708</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それで、
ウンディーネんとこへ
行けんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Can we go to Undine's place now?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>45</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289804</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_046Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、北の海の&lt;Red&gt;浸食洞&lt;White&gt;の
立ち入り許可証だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes. Travelling north you'll find &lt;Red&gt;Limestone Cavern&lt;White&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>46</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_047&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>サンキュー、
バジルさん！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you, Basil!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>47</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_048&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとうございます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you very much.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>48</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290104</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_049Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いや。頑張りなよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's nothing. Do your worst.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>49</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290104</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_050Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>将来、君たちに目指すものが
見つかるよう応援しているからね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you need any help in the future, just ask me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>49</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290164</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_051&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gotcha!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>51</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_052Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Claus&gt;、
約束、忘れないでくれよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Claus&gt;. Don't forget your promise.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>52</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_053&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ん、ああ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mmm? Sure.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>53</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290420</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_054&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うぉし、
&lt;Dio&gt;くん、&lt;Mel&gt;ちゃん、
精霊さんに会いに行こうぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right! &lt;Dio&gt;, &lt;Mel&gt;! It's time to give the
Spirit a visit it'll never forget!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>54</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290480</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_055&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おうっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>55</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290544</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_050_056&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>は、はい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-Yes...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>56</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
